sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Router as TGIS Router (Rust)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC TLS/mTLS
    participant HTTP as TGIS HTTP Server<br/>3000/TCP
    participant Batcher as Continuous Batcher<br/>(in-process)
    participant Shard0 as Python Shard 0<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant ShardN as Python Shard N<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1
    participant NCCL as NCCL<br/>29500/TCP plaintext

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (GenerationService.Generate)

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>Router: Forward gRPC<br/>8033/TCP, TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate request params<br/>(max tokens, sequence length)
    Router->>Router: Tokenize input text
    Router->>Batcher: Enqueue in batch queue<br/>(weight-aware scheduling)
    Batcher->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>UDS gRPC, plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: Forward pass (prefill)
    Shard0->>NCCL: allreduce (multi-GPU)<br/>29500/TCP, plaintext
    NCCL->>ShardN: Tensor sync
    Shard0-->>Batcher: Prefill result + KV cache
    loop NextToken decode loop
        Batcher->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>UDS gRPC, plaintext
        Shard0->>GPU: Forward pass (decode)
        Shard0-->>Batcher: Next token + stop signal
    end
    Batcher-->>Router: Complete response
    Router-->>KServe: gRPC response<br/>TLS/mTLS
    KServe-->>Client: JSON/gRPC response<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (GenerationService.GenerateStream)

    Client->>Router: GenerateStream RPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate + Tokenize
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>UDS gRPC, plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: Forward pass (prefill)
    Router-->>Client: Stream first token<br/>gRPC server-stream
    loop Token-by-token streaming
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>UDS gRPC, plaintext
        Shard0->>GPU: Forward pass (decode)
        Router-->>Client: Stream token<br/>gRPC server-stream
    end

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Health Check

    participant Kubelet as Kubernetes Kubelet
    Kubelet->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>3000/TCP HTTP, no TLS
    HTTP->>Shard0: Health RPC<br/>UDS gRPC, plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA alloc test
    GPU-->>Shard0: OK
    Shard0-->>HTTP: Healthy
    HTTP-->>Kubelet: 200 OK
